===Deploy===
Lihat 
* Konfigurasi File [[app.yaml|https://cloud.google.com/appengine/docs/standard/nodejs/config/appref]]
* Gunakan [[npm run deploy|https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/nodejs-docs-samples/tree/master/appengine/hello-world/standard]]

```bash
#gcloud app deploy --version=v1-1
env: standard
service: mobnile
runtime: nodejs10
instance_class: F1

env_variables:
  BACKEND_URL: 'https://product-dot-chetabahana.appspot.com'

handlers:
  - url: /.*
    script: auto
```

